《'''黑幫追殺令'''》（{{lang-en|''The Family''}}）<ref name="The Family">{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/first-look-at-hugh-jackman-jake-gyllenhaal-in-prisoners-and-robert-de-niro-michelle-pfeiffer-in-malavita-20130530 |title=First Look At Hugh Jackman & Jake Gyllenhaal In 'Prisoners' And Robert De Niro & Michelle Pfeiffer In 'The Family' |access-date=2013-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608081837/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/first-look-at-hugh-jackman-jake-gyllenhaal-in-prisoners-and-robert-de-niro-michelle-pfeiffer-in-malavita-20130530 |archive-date=2013-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>是一部2013年法国黑色喜剧片，{{link-en|Tonino Benacquista|Tonino Benacquista}}编剧、[[洛·比桑|洛·比桑]]执导、[[羅拔·迪尼路|羅拔·迪尼路]]主演。根据{{link-en|Tonino Benacquista|Tonino Benacquista}}所著的法國小说《''Malavita''》改编而成<ref>{{cite book|author=Tonino Benacquista|title=Badfellas|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=DQqbQAAACAAJ|accessdate=10 August 2012|date=1 January 2010|publisher=Bitter Lemon Press|isbn=978-1-904738-43-5|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231162714/http://books.google.com/books?id=DQqbQAAACAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。北美由[[相对论传媒|相对论传媒]]发行于9月13日上映。

==剧情==
讲述一个原名为曼佐尼（Manzoni）、处于“[[证人|证人]]保护计划”下的[[黑手党|黑手党]]家庭迁居到[[诺曼底|诺曼底]]后、更名为布雷克（Blake），开始努力适应新生活的故事。

